1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:31,430 --> 00:01:34,940
[Road Home]

3
00:01:35,289 --> 00:01:37,840
[Episode 9]

4
00:01:38,890 --> 00:01:39,620
Are you busy?

5
00:01:46,140 --> 00:01:47,200
I'm on leave today.

6
00:01:50,430 --> 00:01:52,020
Is Qin Xiaonan okay?

7
00:02:04,030 --> 00:02:04,580
He said

8
00:02:05,180 --> 00:02:05,980
he misses you.

9
00:02:09,460 --> 00:02:10,690
Great. Let me tell you.

10
00:02:10,690 --> 00:02:11,820
Fishing there is...

11
00:02:12,540 --> 00:02:14,120
Chen. Do you want to go fishing?

12
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,020
Let's go together.

13
00:02:15,020 --> 00:02:15,580
No.

14
00:02:16,340 --> 00:02:17,130
Okay, let's go.

15
00:02:17,130 --> 00:02:17,930
That place...

16
00:02:19,060 --> 00:02:19,390
Wait.

17
00:02:20,220 --> 00:02:20,780
What?

18
00:02:21,500 --> 00:02:22,680
Do you want to go fishing?

19
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:22,960
Yes.

20
00:02:24,030 --> 00:02:24,450
But

21
00:02:24,720 --> 00:02:25,780
I'm okay if I don't.

22
00:02:26,790 --> 00:02:27,590
Go ahead then.

23
00:02:27,810 --> 00:02:29,030
It's Chinese New Year.

24
00:02:29,030 --> 00:02:30,490
It's rare to be on holiday.

25
00:02:30,579 --> 00:02:31,380
Not at all.

26
00:02:32,130 --> 00:02:34,300
I've been on winter vacation for a long time.

27
00:02:34,300 --> 00:02:35,160
Just do as I say.

28
00:02:35,950 --> 00:02:37,480
Boys should exercise more.

29
00:02:39,820 --> 00:02:40,370
Come on.

30
00:02:41,300 --> 00:02:43,450
Take him to a nice dinner after fishing.

31
00:02:43,450 --> 00:02:44,100
No problem.

32
00:02:44,100 --> 00:02:44,960
Leave him to us.

33
00:02:45,100 --> 00:02:45,990
Come back later.

34
00:02:45,990 --> 00:02:46,320
Okay.

35
00:02:47,100 --> 00:02:47,630
Let's go.

36
00:04:00,570 --> 00:04:01,090
Chen.

37
00:04:01,700 --> 00:04:03,140
You've been standing here for half an hour.

38
00:04:03,140 --> 00:04:04,070
Aren't you cold?

39
00:04:10,370 --> 00:04:10,900
I'm here.

40
00:04:18,700 --> 00:04:19,230
Drive in.

41
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:21,320
Let me take a look at your car.

42
00:04:24,220 --> 00:04:24,750
Come out.

43
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:25,860
I'll drive.

44
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:45,220
[Lu Zheng Automobile Repair]

45
00:04:47,340 --> 00:04:47,780
Miss.

46
00:04:48,659 --> 00:04:50,390
Have you gotten your car fixed?

47
00:04:51,790 --> 00:04:53,320
Yes, it's fixed. Thank you.

48
00:05:00,380 --> 00:05:01,700
It's driving a little crooked.

49
00:05:01,700 --> 00:05:02,900
The noise is loud too.

50
00:05:07,310 --> 00:05:07,970
Soda water.

51
00:05:10,940 --> 00:05:11,580
Later, I'll check

52
00:05:11,580 --> 00:05:12,640
your tire pressure

53
00:05:13,010 --> 00:05:14,140
and wheel alignment

54
00:05:16,540 --> 00:05:18,070
before checking the tires.

55
00:05:20,060 --> 00:05:21,180
Did it shake very badly

56
00:05:21,180 --> 00:05:22,740
when you warmed up the car this morning?

57
00:05:22,740 --> 00:05:23,820
Not too bad.

58
00:05:26,210 --> 00:05:27,180
What do you mean?

59
00:05:27,860 --> 00:05:29,320
Didn't you drive this car?

60
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:32,380
I don't usually drive.

61
00:05:32,380 --> 00:05:33,600
I go on business trips very often.

62
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,790
Is there a problem?

63
00:05:36,180 --> 00:05:38,370
There's a problem with the valve train.

64
00:05:38,370 --> 00:05:39,450
Just drive on the expressway more often

65
00:05:39,450 --> 00:05:40,909
and it'll sort itself out.

66
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,250
You're quite good at lying.

67
00:05:44,010 --> 00:05:45,470
What did I lie to you about?

68
00:05:45,940 --> 00:05:47,300
Last year, someone fooled me

69
00:05:47,300 --> 00:05:48,630
into aligning my tires.

70
00:05:48,860 --> 00:05:50,020
Did they mess up?

71
00:05:52,740 --> 00:05:54,400
It's not that they fooled you.

72
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,780
It's because of their technique.

73
00:05:59,060 --> 00:05:59,590
Alright.

74
00:06:00,190 --> 00:06:01,320
I'll leave it to you.

75
00:06:07,140 --> 00:06:08,340
Where's Qin Xiaonan?

76
00:06:09,690 --> 00:06:10,620
He went fishing.

77
00:06:12,780 --> 00:06:14,240
Didn't he say he missed me?

78
00:06:14,410 --> 00:06:15,670
He still went fishing.

79
00:06:16,170 --> 00:06:17,180
He's just a kid.

80
00:06:17,700 --> 00:06:19,900
He doesn't remember the things he says.

81
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:21,300
When will he be back?

82
00:06:21,300 --> 00:06:21,860
I brought him

83
00:06:21,860 --> 00:06:23,190
a lot of delicious food.

84
00:06:23,500 --> 00:06:24,230
I don't know.

85
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:26,960
He should be back quite late.

86
00:06:32,740 --> 00:06:33,500
What is this?

87
00:06:36,340 --> 00:06:37,140
Ring spanner.

88
00:06:38,220 --> 00:06:38,800
What about that one?

89
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:39,330
That one.

90
00:06:41,300 --> 00:06:42,159
Socket wrench.

91
00:06:43,090 --> 00:06:43,890
What is it for?

92
00:06:45,500 --> 00:06:46,180
It turns

93
00:06:46,860 --> 00:06:47,659
the bolts

94
00:06:48,470 --> 00:06:49,070
on tires.

95
00:06:54,050 --> 00:06:54,480
Go in.

96
00:06:55,400 --> 00:06:57,060
Don't we need to check the car?

97
00:06:57,250 --> 00:06:58,780
We'll do it in the afternoon.

98
00:06:58,780 --> 00:07:00,290
It's too cold in the garage.

99
00:07:00,290 --> 00:07:01,290
It's warm inside.

100
00:07:02,060 --> 00:07:02,390
Okay.

101
00:07:07,030 --> 00:07:11,370
[Finance Room]

102
00:07:20,950 --> 00:07:21,350
Hello?

103
00:07:21,660 --> 00:07:22,500
Your son brought a girl

104
00:07:22,500 --> 00:07:23,300
to the garage.

105
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:28,410
It's messy because of the kid.

106
00:07:28,500 --> 00:07:29,560
I tried tidying up.

107
00:07:30,630 --> 00:07:32,140
It used to be even messier.

108
00:07:46,780 --> 00:07:47,940
I remember the first time

109
00:07:47,940 --> 00:07:48,980
I came here,

110
00:07:49,409 --> 00:07:51,409
there was a pile of test papers here.

111
00:07:52,820 --> 00:07:54,340
I still get scared when I hear the words

112
00:07:54,340 --> 00:07:55,140
"test paper."

113
00:07:55,620 --> 00:07:57,620
I did too many of them in high school.

114
00:07:59,460 --> 00:08:00,720
Can you understand it?

115
00:08:02,060 --> 00:08:03,030
Of course.

116
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:04,840
It's such a simple question.

117
00:08:08,170 --> 00:08:09,250
I remember that in our time,

118
00:08:09,250 --> 00:08:10,110
the math papers

119
00:08:10,260 --> 00:08:11,500
were carved and printed

120
00:08:11,500 --> 00:08:13,020
by the teachers themselves.

121
00:08:13,020 --> 00:08:13,740
Every time I finished one,

122
00:08:13,740 --> 00:08:15,340
my hand would have blue smudges on it.

123
00:08:15,340 --> 00:08:17,000
I couldn't even wash them off.

124
00:08:17,100 --> 00:08:17,560
Really?

125
00:08:19,060 --> 00:08:20,070
I bought my test papers

126
00:08:20,070 --> 00:08:21,270
at the school gate.

127
00:08:22,740 --> 00:08:24,240
Our teacher was thrifty.

128
00:08:24,540 --> 00:08:25,940
He carved it all himself.

129
00:08:27,060 --> 00:08:27,860
I remember

130
00:08:27,860 --> 00:08:29,140
my math teacher

131
00:08:29,140 --> 00:08:30,020
was already 60

132
00:08:30,020 --> 00:08:31,020
when he taught me.

133
00:08:31,890 --> 00:08:33,419
I wonder how he's doing now.

134
00:08:33,669 --> 00:08:34,600
Is he doing well?

135
00:08:48,520 --> 00:08:49,780
The first time I saw you

136
00:08:50,130 --> 00:08:51,190
at the gas station,

137
00:08:52,410 --> 00:08:54,070
I didn't dare to approach you.

138
00:08:56,500 --> 00:08:57,830
You still look the same,

139
00:09:00,540 --> 00:09:02,200
but you've suddenly grown up.

140
00:09:04,900 --> 00:09:05,830
The door is open.

141
00:09:38,430 --> 00:09:38,890
Lu—

142
00:09:45,020 --> 00:09:46,060
I...

143
00:09:47,130 --> 00:09:48,490
I came back in a hurry

144
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:49,980
to see Aunt Gui Xiao.

145
00:09:51,780 --> 00:09:53,340
It's not enough just to have fish.

146
00:09:53,340 --> 00:09:54,470
We need vegetables.

147
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:57,440
Yes.

148
00:09:59,370 --> 00:10:00,900
Let's go grocery shopping.

149
00:10:01,020 --> 00:10:01,460
Okay.

150
00:10:25,140 --> 00:10:27,070
Hello, are you looking for Lu Chen?

151
00:10:28,130 --> 00:10:28,850
You are?

152
00:10:29,800 --> 00:10:31,080
I'm his classmate.

153
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:32,780
His ex-classmate.

154
00:10:35,580 --> 00:10:36,710
Auntie, who are you?

155
00:10:37,140 --> 00:10:38,340
I’m Lu Chen’s mother.

156
00:10:41,220 --> 00:10:42,080
Hello, Auntie.

157
00:10:42,940 --> 00:10:43,870
Where is Lu Chen?

158
00:10:44,180 --> 00:10:45,100
He went out to buy groceries.

159
00:10:45,100 --> 00:10:46,160
He'll be back soon.

160
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:50,460
He left you here alone

161
00:10:50,780 --> 00:10:52,110
to go grocery shopping?

162
00:10:54,290 --> 00:10:55,260
Have a seat.

163
00:10:55,570 --> 00:10:56,630
I'll wait outside.

164
00:10:56,660 --> 00:10:57,380
It's okay.

165
00:10:57,400 --> 00:10:58,040
Sit down.

166
00:11:05,460 --> 00:11:06,720
Why don't you sit down?

167
00:11:11,040 --> 00:11:12,040
What's your name?

168
00:11:12,170 --> 00:11:12,700
Gui Xiao.

169
00:11:14,380 --> 00:11:16,440
"Gui" as in return, "Xiao" as in dawn.

170
00:11:20,560 --> 00:11:21,890
Auntie, let me help you.

171
00:11:22,300 --> 00:11:22,970
It's okay.

172
00:11:23,230 --> 00:11:24,130
You are our guest.

173
00:11:24,130 --> 00:11:24,770
Sit down.

174
00:11:34,590 --> 00:11:35,380
Auntie, I’ll leave you alone.

175
00:11:35,380 --> 00:11:36,770
I need to make a call.

176
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:05,400
Miss.

177
00:12:06,210 --> 00:12:06,940
Are you cold?

178
00:12:07,900 --> 00:12:09,160
I'm fine. I'm not cold.

179
00:12:11,970 --> 00:12:12,300
Here.

180
00:12:12,940 --> 00:12:13,870
Come sit inside.

181
00:12:14,800 --> 00:12:15,800
Will I be a bother?

182
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:17,060
I was hoping

183
00:12:17,060 --> 00:12:18,720
someone would come talk to me.

184
00:12:21,580 --> 00:12:22,780
Sit there. It's warm.

185
00:12:25,750 --> 00:12:26,610
Do you want some tea?

186
00:12:26,610 --> 00:12:27,530
No, thanks.

187
00:12:30,510 --> 00:12:33,630
Did you meet Lu Chen through car repair?

188
00:12:36,380 --> 00:12:38,140
No, we were classmates.

189
00:12:38,860 --> 00:12:40,390
Middle school classmates.

190
00:12:46,350 --> 00:12:47,550
Lu Chen, you're here?

191
00:12:47,630 --> 00:12:49,210
You bought so many vegetables.

192
00:12:49,210 --> 00:12:50,540
Do you have guests over?

193
00:12:52,150 --> 00:12:52,950
Give me a big one.

194
00:12:52,950 --> 00:12:53,300
Okay.

195
00:12:56,330 --> 00:12:57,390
Give me half a catty

196
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:58,350
of prawns.

197
00:12:59,340 --> 00:13:00,140
Prawns are expensive

198
00:13:00,140 --> 00:13:01,160
these days.

199
00:13:01,650 --> 00:13:03,120
It's going to be Chinese New Year soon.

200
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:04,260
It's expensive for me to get them too.

201
00:13:04,260 --> 00:13:05,460
The price has gone up.

202
00:13:05,870 --> 00:13:06,800
I have no choice.

203
00:13:07,100 --> 00:13:08,550
-It’s okay, go ahead.
-I'm not scamming you.

204
00:13:08,550 --> 00:13:09,020
Okay.

205
00:13:15,990 --> 00:13:17,120
Give me another one.

206
00:13:17,350 --> 00:13:18,350
Pick the best one.

207
00:13:23,330 --> 00:13:23,810
Auntie.

208
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:26,250
You're leaving?

209
00:13:27,860 --> 00:13:30,050
I've changed the bedsheets, I should go.

210
00:13:30,050 --> 00:13:31,820
He doesn't want me around.

211
00:13:37,500 --> 00:13:39,030
If it's convenient for you,

212
00:13:39,760 --> 00:13:40,880
come with him to have a meal

213
00:13:40,880 --> 00:13:41,760
at my house.

214
00:13:43,090 --> 00:13:44,220
Let that kid

215
00:13:44,570 --> 00:13:45,410
come too.

216
00:13:48,500 --> 00:13:50,500
I'll let him know when he comes back.

217
00:13:51,540 --> 00:13:52,060
See you.

218
00:13:52,930 --> 00:13:53,530
Take care.

219
00:14:33,390 --> 00:14:34,520
Why did you come out?

220
00:14:37,290 --> 00:14:38,760
Your mother came just now.

221
00:14:39,900 --> 00:14:41,320
She seemed a little unhappy.

222
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:42,830
I was afraid I might say something wrong,

223
00:14:42,830 --> 00:14:44,160
so I came out for a while.

224
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:46,960
Did she bully you?

225
00:14:48,340 --> 00:14:48,820
No.

226
00:14:50,140 --> 00:14:51,340
Your mother is nice.

227
00:14:52,300 --> 00:14:53,900
She even asked Qin Xiaonan and me

228
00:14:53,900 --> 00:14:55,160
to go eat at your house.

229
00:14:56,940 --> 00:14:58,190
Are we going?

230
00:15:00,060 --> 00:15:00,990
Do you want to go?

231
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:07,060
I bought so many things.

232
00:15:07,060 --> 00:15:08,290
It's a waste if we don't eat them.

233
00:15:08,290 --> 00:15:08,750
Go on in.

234
00:15:10,430 --> 00:15:11,650
If I don't go,

235
00:15:11,850 --> 00:15:13,580
shouldn't we explain it to her?

236
00:15:13,750 --> 00:15:14,420
I think

237
00:15:14,720 --> 00:15:16,330
she really wants you to go back.

238
00:15:16,330 --> 00:15:16,930
It's okay.

239
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:18,500
I'll talk to her later.

240
00:15:20,060 --> 00:15:20,660
Chen.

241
00:15:20,810 --> 00:15:22,010
Someone is making trouble inside.

242
00:15:22,010 --> 00:15:23,360
I can't handle it.

243
00:15:24,720 --> 00:15:25,380
Wait here.

244
00:15:27,100 --> 00:15:28,080
Don't touch the bag.

245
00:15:28,080 --> 00:15:29,170
The water on it is dirty.

246
00:15:29,170 --> 00:15:30,030
It's not clean.

247
00:15:31,240 --> 00:15:33,040
You must give us an explanation.

248
00:15:33,140 --> 00:15:33,980
Calm down.

249
00:15:34,010 --> 00:15:35,360
Ask your boss to come out.

250
00:15:35,360 --> 00:15:36,070
Wait here.

251
00:15:36,100 --> 00:15:37,500
I'll go in and take a look.

252
00:15:40,170 --> 00:15:41,260
What are you looking at?

253
00:15:41,260 --> 00:15:41,940
Fix it!

254
00:15:43,700 --> 00:15:45,540
Why did you buy two big fish?

255
00:15:45,970 --> 00:15:47,500
Isn't there a small one too?

256
00:15:47,670 --> 00:15:48,600
Uncle Lu said

257
00:15:48,900 --> 00:15:50,040
he was scared you might want to eat a big fish

258
00:15:50,040 --> 00:15:51,300
and we didn't have one.

259
00:15:55,620 --> 00:15:56,020
Here.

260
00:16:03,860 --> 00:16:04,430
Sir.

261
00:16:07,920 --> 00:16:08,860
Can you

262
00:16:08,860 --> 00:16:10,120
get us some warm water?

263
00:16:10,450 --> 00:16:11,880
Okay. You go in first.

264
00:16:11,910 --> 00:16:13,240
I'll get you some water.

265
00:16:13,390 --> 00:16:14,320
Okay, thank you.

266
00:16:18,140 --> 00:16:19,020
Thank you.

267
00:16:19,900 --> 00:16:21,160
You're welcome.

268
00:16:21,180 --> 00:16:22,770
I'm happy that you came to chat with me.

269
00:16:22,770 --> 00:16:23,970
Come here more often.

270
00:16:24,440 --> 00:16:25,640
She will come often.

271
00:16:26,460 --> 00:16:27,280
I'll get going then.

272
00:16:27,280 --> 00:16:27,810
Go ahead.

273
00:16:29,930 --> 00:16:30,860
Wash your hands.

274
00:16:41,820 --> 00:16:42,750
Sister-in-law?

275
00:16:43,020 --> 00:16:43,560
Hai Dong?

276
00:16:43,600 --> 00:16:45,070
We've finally met.

277
00:16:45,700 --> 00:16:46,740
Meng Xiaoshan told me about you.

278
00:16:46,740 --> 00:16:47,540
Lu Chen told me about you.

279
00:16:47,540 --> 00:16:48,900
But I didn't get to see you.

280
00:16:48,900 --> 00:16:49,910
When did you get here?

281
00:16:49,910 --> 00:16:50,430
In the morning,

282
00:16:50,430 --> 00:16:51,560
around ten o’clock.

283
00:16:51,880 --> 00:16:53,360
Lu Chen didn't tell me. He's hiding you from me.

284
00:16:53,360 --> 00:16:53,980
If he'd told me,

285
00:16:53,980 --> 00:16:55,510
I'd have come immediately.

286
00:16:56,900 --> 00:16:57,530
Wait a minute.

287
00:16:57,530 --> 00:16:58,670
There are some punks outside

288
00:16:58,670 --> 00:16:59,260
causing trouble.

289
00:16:59,260 --> 00:17:00,300
I'll go take a look.

290
00:17:00,300 --> 00:17:01,820
I'll get rid of the water for you.

291
00:17:01,820 --> 00:17:02,180
Okay.

292
00:17:02,180 --> 00:17:03,240
Take this away too.

293
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:03,570
Okay.

294
00:17:10,430 --> 00:17:11,260
You're not leaving tonight, right?

295
00:17:11,260 --> 00:17:12,190
Stay for dinner.

296
00:17:12,230 --> 00:17:12,880
