00:32:50,470 --> 00:32:52,890
♫Even meteors stop♫

583
00:32:53,630 --> 00:32:56,380
♫Love songs are popular♫

584
00:32:55,910 --> 00:32:56,640
Do you see it?

585
00:32:56,900 --> 00:32:59,110
♫I'll sing for you♫

586
00:32:59,670 --> 00:33:02,620
♫We need to cultivate our relationship♫

587
00:33:03,120 --> 00:33:05,780
♫I believe you can do it♫

588
00:33:05,930 --> 00:33:06,730
Yes.

589
00:33:08,170 --> 00:33:09,970
Aren't you afraid of being seen?

590
00:33:18,750 --> 00:33:20,280
What's wrong? Did you fall?

591
00:33:21,030 --> 00:33:22,050
Someone is coming.

592
00:33:22,050 --> 00:33:22,780
I'm leaving.

593
00:33:36,170 --> 00:33:36,900
Sleep early.

594
00:34:18,840 --> 00:34:19,800
Uncle Lu.

595
00:34:20,250 --> 00:34:21,650
I thought you weren't coming back

596
00:34:21,650 --> 00:34:22,889
to sleep tonight.

597
00:34:23,659 --> 00:34:24,860
Where else could I go?

598
00:34:27,139 --> 00:34:28,870
Have you gotten used to it here?

599
00:34:33,699 --> 00:34:34,630
Do you miss home?

600
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:38,880
I've been here for so long.

601
00:34:39,719 --> 00:34:41,449
Why did you only ask me tonight?

602
00:34:51,060 --> 00:34:51,989
Aunt Gui Xiao...

603
00:34:54,699 --> 00:34:55,219
Uncle.

604
00:34:55,670 --> 00:34:56,929
What do you want to ask?

605
00:34:57,650 --> 00:34:58,310
Go to sleep.

606
00:35:07,290 --> 00:35:07,820
What has Aunt Gui Xiao

607
00:35:07,820 --> 00:35:09,020
been doing recently?

608
00:35:12,260 --> 00:35:13,660
I didn't have time to ask.

609
00:35:13,700 --> 00:35:15,100
Do you know about her job?

610
00:35:19,900 --> 00:35:22,900
Is there anything wrong with her work?

611
00:35:23,700 --> 00:35:26,150
Is it against the rules?

612
00:35:26,180 --> 00:35:26,750
No.

613
00:35:27,780 --> 00:35:28,860
I just want to know.

614
00:35:31,870 --> 00:35:33,350
Just ask Aunt Gui Xiao.

615
00:35:37,930 --> 00:35:39,030
It's 2 a.m.

616
00:35:39,270 --> 00:35:39,930
How do I ask?

617
00:35:42,030 --> 00:35:43,600
Ask her tomorrow.

618
00:35:49,220 --> 00:35:50,200
I'm not sure.

619
00:35:52,900 --> 00:35:55,730
I think she's an investor.

620
00:35:57,380 --> 00:36:00,110
She has money and looks for projects everywhere.

621
00:36:00,780 --> 00:36:05,180
She told her colleagues she was investing in...

622
00:36:05,730 --> 00:36:07,600
in educational...

623
00:36:08,980 --> 00:36:10,290
educational...

624
00:36:11,970 --> 00:36:12,890
new energy?

625
00:36:14,180 --> 00:36:15,180
I think so.

626
00:36:15,630 --> 00:36:16,290
Go to sleep.

627
00:36:18,770 --> 00:36:19,370
Your hand.

628
00:36:34,400 --> 00:36:35,400
Get up.

629
00:36:35,640 --> 00:36:36,970
You're going to be late.

630
00:36:37,400 --> 00:36:38,480
Stop it.

631
00:36:38,580 --> 00:36:39,420
I’m sleepy.

632
00:36:42,820 --> 00:36:44,020
Lu Chen is here

633
00:36:44,020 --> 00:36:45,620
to pick you up to go to school.

634
00:36:52,400 --> 00:36:52,950
I want...

635
00:36:53,490 --> 00:36:55,500
My flight is at twelve.

636
00:36:55,610 --> 00:36:57,010
Let me sleep until eight.

637
00:36:58,180 --> 00:36:59,220
Why would I lie to you?

638
00:36:59,220 --> 00:37:00,750
Lu Chen brought breakfast.

639
00:37:26,760 --> 00:37:27,290
Morning.

640
00:37:29,640 --> 00:37:30,700
I bought it for you.

641
00:37:37,780 --> 00:37:38,620
The auntie outside the school gate

642
00:37:38,620 --> 00:37:39,820
opened her own store.

643
00:37:40,260 --> 00:37:41,320
It tastes the same.

644
00:37:46,410 --> 00:37:47,470
It's still hot.

645
00:37:49,540 --> 00:37:50,400
Have you eaten?

646
00:37:51,180 --> 00:37:52,350
I ate at the garage.

647
00:37:52,880 --> 00:37:54,810
I didn't have time to eat on the way.

648
00:38:00,270 --> 00:38:01,800
I'm going back to work soon.

649
00:38:02,020 --> 00:38:03,390
There's a secret mission.

650
00:38:03,390 --> 00:38:05,650
I won't be able to use my phone for a while.

651
00:38:10,590 --> 00:38:12,520
The nature of my work is a bit different.

652
00:38:12,520 --> 00:38:14,320
I become uncontactable at times

653
00:38:14,840 --> 00:38:16,500
and cannot explain anything.

654
00:38:16,510 --> 00:38:17,970
I'm telling you in advance

655
00:38:17,990 --> 00:38:19,050
overthink things.

656
00:38:27,400 --> 00:38:27,860
Well...

657
00:38:28,680 --> 00:38:29,540
I'll be off now.

658
00:38:38,110 --> 00:38:39,170
You're still here?

659
00:38:42,530 --> 00:38:43,380
It was so busy

660
00:38:43,910 --> 00:38:44,680
this time.

661
00:38:45,440 --> 00:38:46,570
Let's talk properly

662
00:38:47,580 --> 00:38:49,780
when you come back from your business trip.

663
00:38:49,780 --> 00:38:50,440
About what?

664
00:38:54,750 --> 00:38:55,450
Your job.

665
00:38:55,980 --> 00:38:56,660
My job.

666
00:38:57,280 --> 00:38:58,540
My family background.

667
00:38:59,220 --> 00:38:59,860
The situation

668
00:38:59,860 --> 00:39:01,190
after my transfer back.

669
00:39:01,500 --> 00:39:02,180
My salary

670
00:39:02,850 --> 00:39:04,180
and my personal assets.

671
00:39:05,420 --> 00:39:06,630
When we were in school,

672
00:39:06,630 --> 00:39:08,410
I didn't tell you much about these.

673
00:39:08,410 --> 00:39:10,470
I want to make them clear this time.

674
00:39:15,330 --> 00:39:16,460
You're thoughtful.

675
00:39:16,540 --> 00:39:18,070
You should make them clear.

676
00:39:22,220 --> 00:39:22,830
Of course,

677
00:39:22,850 --> 00:39:23,620
if you

678
00:39:23,650 --> 00:39:24,650
just want to date,

679
00:39:24,680 --> 00:39:25,320
then it's not necessary.

680
00:39:25,320 --> 00:39:26,440
There's no need to say.

681
00:39:26,440 --> 00:39:27,550
It's good to retain

682
00:39:27,580 --> 00:39:28,690
a bit of the mystery.

683
00:39:28,690 --> 00:39:29,530
Go to work.

684
00:39:29,740 --> 00:39:31,140
I'm going too after I eat.

685
00:39:31,990 --> 00:39:32,320
Okay.

686
00:39:33,410 --> 00:39:34,870
We'll talk about it later.

687
00:39:38,980 --> 00:39:39,710
I’m leaving.

688
00:39:53,850 --> 00:39:55,710
Does your dad know Lu Chen is back?

689
00:39:57,260 --> 00:39:58,590
I don’t want to tell him.

690
00:40:06,150 --> 00:40:10,420
[Hongrun Chenghua]

691
00:40:12,370 --> 00:40:12,780
I thought

692
00:40:12,780 --> 00:40:14,780
you would wait for me at the airport.

693
00:40:14,820 --> 00:40:16,420
I saw that I still had some time,

694
00:40:16,420 --> 00:40:18,820
so I came back to attend the weekly meeting.

695
00:40:21,200 --> 00:40:22,750
You two. Tell me

696
00:40:22,780 --> 00:40:24,380
about your recent projects.

697
00:40:29,360 --> 00:40:30,420
Pass me the agenda.

698
00:40:34,130 --> 00:40:34,860
You go first.

699
00:40:34,880 --> 00:40:35,990
I'll tell you one by one.

700
00:40:35,990 --> 00:40:36,320
Okay.

701
00:40:36,710 --> 00:40:38,220
They insist that the shareholders

702
00:40:38,220 --> 00:40:39,620
should have veto rights.

703
00:40:39,800 --> 00:40:40,550
I told them

704
00:40:40,590 --> 00:40:41,800
I can't promise them something like that,

705
00:40:41,800 --> 00:40:42,860
and that the bosses on both sides

706
00:40:42,860 --> 00:40:44,210
need to discuss this directly.

707
00:40:44,210 --> 00:40:44,980
Make an appointment

708
00:40:44,980 --> 00:40:46,840
for a teleconference with Mr. Wu.

709
00:40:47,290 --> 00:40:48,230
After the secretary confirms it,

710
00:40:48,230 --> 00:40:49,430
email the other party

711
00:40:49,510 --> 00:40:50,590
and CC Mr. Wu and me.

712
00:40:54,880 --> 00:40:56,210
Also, they think

713
00:40:56,240 --> 00:40:57,920
the minimum of 13% of shares

714
00:40:57,940 --> 00:40:58,500
is too low.

715
00:40:58,500 --> 00:41:02,160
They're requesting a directly proportionate capital increase.

716
00:41:02,800 --> 00:41:03,350
We have been dealing with this

717
00:41:03,350 --> 00:41:05,020
for two weeks.

718
00:41:08,550 --> 00:41:09,300
How about this?

719
00:41:09,300 --> 00:41:10,290
Delete the clause on the contract

720
00:41:10,290 --> 00:41:11,570
that precludes capital increase

721
00:41:11,570 --> 00:41:12,940
and proceed with the negotiations.

722
00:41:12,940 --> 00:41:13,270
Okay.

723
00:41:14,540 --> 00:41:16,200
The bottom line I'm giving you

724
00:41:16,460 --> 00:41:17,680
is that we can add a clause for capital increase

725
00:41:17,680 --> 00:41:18,860
into the contract,

726
00:41:19,450 --> 00:41:22,380
but it cannot stipulate any specific requirements.

727
00:41:22,490 --> 00:41:23,890
For instance, terms like

728
00:41:24,300 --> 00:41:25,600
"directly proportionate"

729
00:41:25,600 --> 00:41:27,400
must not appear in the contract.

730
00:41:28,450 --> 00:41:29,050
Remember.

731
00:41:29,850 --> 00:41:30,360
We can only

732
00:41:30,360 --> 00:41:32,330
reveal our bottom line

733
00:41:32,490 --> 00:41:34,190
after at least three rounds of negotiation.

734
00:41:34,190 --> 00:41:34,520
Okay.

735
00:41:35,940 --> 00:41:36,870
Let me teach you.

736
00:41:37,610 --> 00:41:39,580
Every time the negotiations reach a stalemate,

737
00:41:39,580 --> 00:41:40,350
just say,

738
00:41:41,050 --> 00:41:42,650
"I can't make this decision.

739
00:41:42,740 --> 00:41:43,800
Let me ask my boss."

740
00:41:44,580 --> 00:41:46,910
Then, answer them the next day.

741
00:41:48,030 --> 00:41:50,180
If that doesn't work, tell them,

742
00:41:51,740 --> 00:41:53,620
"My boss is very unaccommodating.

743
00:41:53,620 --> 00:41:55,130
She's very difficult to talk to.

744
00:41:55,130 --> 00:41:56,970
I'll try to persuade her again."

745
00:41:57,750 --> 00:41:58,310
Yes.

746
00:41:58,330 --> 00:41:59,330
Blame it all on me.

747
00:41:59,710 --> 00:42:00,350
I am here

748
00:42:00,410 --> 00:42:01,610
to act as your shield.

749
00:42:02,690 --> 00:42:03,420
Don't worry.

750
00:42:03,440 --> 00:42:04,690
I won't take it to heart

751
00:42:04,690 --> 00:42:07,220
no matter how many bad things you say about me.

752
00:42:20,040 --> 00:42:20,440
Dad.

753
00:42:23,270 --> 00:42:24,330
I'm at the airport.

754
00:42:38,700 --> 00:42:39,570
My dad is here.
